article.headline: Yale secures 80-60 victory over Harvard

images.name: Yale Coasts Past Harvard in Ivy Play  - Via Ivy League
images.caption: Danny Wolf and Bez Mbeng Net Double-Doubles to lead the Bulldogs

article.story: NEW HAVEN, Conn. -- — Danny Wolf scored 16 points as Yale beat Harvard 80-60 on Saturday night. Wolf added 10 rebounds and five assists for the Bulldogs (20-8, 11-2 Ivy League). Nick Townsend finished 6 of 7 from the field to add 14 points. John Poulakidas shot 5 for 11, including 2 for 6 from beyond the arc to finish with 12 points, while adding six rebounds. Louis Lesmond and Chisom Okpara each finished with 11 points for the Crimson (14-12, 5-8). Malik Mack also recorded eight points, six rebounds and five assists. NEXT UP Yale next plays Saturday against Brown at home, and Harvard will visit Dartmouth on Tuesday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
